Menard
------

Menard is web-tool to manage ocr-scans together with bibliographical 
information from zotero. It provides a full-text search within the
metadata and the ocr-files and a viewer in the browser to read the stored scans.

On the server-side it uses Java 8 to provide the needed REST-APIs. To build
it use ant and call "ant build", do create a RPM-file call "ant deploy".